Maitland Ward https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maitland_Ward 0 Maitland Ward (born Ashley Maitland Welkos; February 3, 1977) is an American Cosplay Star and former television actress. She is known for playing Rachel McGuire on the ABC original series Boy Meets World and Jessica Forrester on the CBS soap opera The Bold and the Beautiful.
